quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,70,"When he said to his father and his people: "
  26,71,"They said: "
  26,72,"He said: "
  27,43,"And that which she used to worship besides Allâh has prevented her (from Islâm), for she was of a disbelieving people."
  27,44,"It was said to her: "
  27,45,"And indeed We sent to Thamûd their brother Sâlih, saying: "
  28,16,"He said: "
  28,17,"He said: "
  28,18,"So he became afraid, looking about in the city (waiting as to what will be the result of his crime of killing), when behold, the man who had sought his help the day before, called for his help (again). Mûsâ (Moses) said to him: "